{"tid":40637,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"囡 囡 快 踏 入 反 叛 期  梁 詠 琪 睇 書 學 教 女","createTime":"2016-12-15T10:21:37.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T11:24:52.000Z","uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"75d8156c21ef1ae8ec29694662b249c803c11bca","tid":40637,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:21:37.000Z","msg":"梁詠琪 (GiGi) 的巡唱令囡囡留下深刻印象，看完深圳頭場後，講足幾星期，GiGi說：「佢話：『Wanna see mama dancing and singing like this.』一見到手機就話要睇Mama dancing，我有時要人肉表演畀佢睇。」她續說：「佢見我有套衫，有蝴蝶喺頭上面，佢又話：『I want some butterflies on my head.』我有首新歌叫《My Little Sofia》，每次聽到佢都掩嘴笑，認得好快。」<br />\n<br />\n囡囡開朗、學習能力高，其實GiGi並沒有刻意催谷，間中才帶她上playgroup，反而着重家庭教育，培養價值觀，常向她提問來引導思考，「有啲周末，爸爸帶佢去睇聖誕燈飾，我做完嘢返屋企，爸爸就會引導佢講成個weekend做咗乜、見到乜，我發現佢好鍾意好似新聞報道咁講一次。」<br />\n<br />\n還有兩個月，囡囡就踏入「Trouble 2」，GiGi暫時不覺女兒反叛，「聽人講係好棘手嘅，但我覺得都係一個過程。佢表達不滿、主見都係正常，始終每個人有佢嘅想法，要畀佢知道我哋知道、尊重佢感受之餘，有一啲rules係一定要跟。」講得頭頭是道，自認經驗不足的她全靠睇書學教女，「情感抒發係唔可以壓制，只能夠control佢嘅自律性、行為。」讓她自由抒發，才有健康童年。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20161213/large/1481626916_bd33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20161213%2Flarge%2F1481626916_bd33.jpg&h=04db1b64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舉行巡場期間，GiGi超掛念囡囡，試過騷前進行視像通話令她狂喊。"},{"pid":"0360fb84b88713ce392d40cd0c52352a981ee2e1","tid":40637,"uid":29880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:22:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>西</strong></span>"},{"pid":"b94f8383f5a5c28fd64ed15056bcc72911aaf1d7","tid":40637,"uid":43804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"搵我？"},{"pid":"7a07ab6666f6ff371f37486cae890f2e46200ae9","tid":40637,"uid":35408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:22:56.000Z","msg":"班"},{"pid":"ddf84bb41ad36f01ed7e582fd9a269cb32127263","tid":40637,"uid":27148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:23:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>西</strong></span></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>班</strong></span>"},{"pid":"cab9629b75e6b98f8a896be70072d759642bdc67","tid":40637,"uid":34647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T10:24:17.000Z","msg":"Sergio藉老公西班牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd442bf0ce7bfcb05b8171e1c16b2f303fffb48b","tid":40637,"uid":56377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}